headline: T. ROWE PRICE EXPERTS SHARE 2025 OUTLOOK FOR GLOBAL FINANCIAL MARKETS
summary: T. Rowe Price held its 42nd annual global market outlook press briefing today, featuring a panel of the firm's investment experts sharing their forecasts for the 2025 global financial markets. Speakers included, Blerina Uruçi, Chief U.S. Economist, Ken Orchard, Head of International Fixed Income, Jennifer Martin, Global Equity Portfolio Specialist, Sébastien Page, Head of Global Multi-Asset and Chief Investment Officer, and Donna Anderson, Global Head of Corporate Governance.
